<br>
Walking closer, Hipp threw up some fronds at the working amazon with a chuckle.  &quot;Here you go, warrior.&quot;  Then she climbed up beside Lysia, dragging up the rest of the fronds with her. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

